## **Underpinning and Renovation Work for Residential Building in London, England**

### **Procurement Details**

*   **Reference Number:** PW-22-01014922
*   **Publication Date:** 2022-11-29
*   **Tender Closing Date:** 2022-12-16T00:00:00
*   **Procurement Category:** Construction Services
*   **Notice Type:** Invitation to Qualify
*   **Procurement Method:** Competitive - Open Bidding

### **Contracting Entity and End User**

*   **Contracting Entity:** Foreign Affairs, Trade And Development (Department Of)
*   **Contact Name:** Tanya DiVirgilio
*   **Contact Title:** n/a
*   **Contact Email:** realproperty-contracts@international.gc.ca
*   **Contact Phone:** 343-573-0472
*   **End User Entities:** Foreign Affairs, Trade And Development (Department Of)
*   **End User Address:** 125 Sussex Dr, Ottawa, Ontario, K1A 0G2, Canada

### **Content**

This procurement is for underpinning and renovation works on a residential building in London, England. The work involves stripping out parts of the ground floor living room, dining room, and kitchen and reinstalling and redecorating the space. The proposed contract duration is three months, and the expected start date will be determined upon contract award.

**Notable Details:**

*   Estimated quantity of commodity: 1
*   Time frame of delivery: 3 months
*   The specified trade agreements for this project are **Canadian Free Trade Agreement (CFTA)**
*   **GSIN Codes:**
    *   *5139A – Construction Services, Not Elsewhere Specified*
    *   *5159B – Other Special Trade Construction Work*
    *   *5177BA – Interior Fit-Up/Renovations*
